        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Supporting Seniors with Opioid Use Disorder Act of 2022</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services to conduct additional outreach regarding opioid use disorder treatment services that are covered under Medicare and to collect relevant data on the utilization of such services.</p>]]>
